column6:
[8:6] Array Precharge Sense Fault
[8]: 1 indicates Array precharge sense fault happened
[7]: Expected array precharge sense value
[6]: Actual array precharge sense value
[5:3] Motor Precharge Fault
[5]: Motor precharge sense fault happened
[4]: Expected motor precharge sense value
[3]: Actual motor precharge sense value
[2:0] Motor Sense Fault
[2]: 1 indicates Motor sense fault happened
[1]: Expected motor sense value
[0]: Actual motor sense value

Timeout fault for either or array or motor precharge
1 if it faulted, 0 if not faulted
[1]: Array precharge timeout
[0]: Motor precharge timeout
